 Acting under this authority, the FTC has exempted the following products from certain FPLA requirements_camera
film; Christmas tree ornaments; replacement bags for vacuum cleaners; chamois; paper table covers; certain cellulose
sponges; candles; and solder. (16 CFR part 501.) 


